@host = http://localhost:5268

### List orders for Acme
GET {{host}}/orders
X-Tenant-Id: acme
Accept: application/json

### List orders for Globex
GET {{host}}/orders
X-Tenant-Id: globex
Accept: application/json

### Show current tenant
GET {{host}}/me
X-Tenant-Id: acme
Accept: application/json

### Health check (no tenant needed)
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Orders without tenant header (should fail)
GET {{host}}/orders
Accept: application/json
